@Andrzej As I was solving this, I thought, well this is going to take some people less than 5 minutes (those who can get one spanning answer in each section straight away), and some people over an hour (those who can't!).

I was the former for the top two sections, both done in a couple of minutes, and then the latter for the bottom section (took me the rest of my 32 minute solve time).

So an interesting, but flawed, format for a grid, I'd say.

@Andrzej 

